  <h1>A4  XML External Entities (XXE)</h1>
  <p class="muted">Vulnerabilities in XML parsers that process untrusted XML.</p>
  <h3>Mitigations</h3>
  <ul><li>Disable external entity resolution; prefer safer formats (JSON) or secure XML parser settings.</li></ul>
  <h3>Where to patch</h3>
  <p>If your app uses XML libraries, ensure parser settings disable DTDs/ENTITIES.</p>
